<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "facebook.jpg", width: 300, alt: 'profile', class: 'profile-img' %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated"
                     role="progressbar"
                     aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                     aria-valuemin="0"
                     aria-valuemax="100"
                     style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>

          <% end %>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000
          years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin</p>

        <p>There are many variations of passages of Lorem Ipsum available, but the majority have suffered alteration in some form, by injected humour, or
          randomised words which don't look even slightly believable. If you are going to use a passage of Lorem Ipsum, you need to be sure.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="jobHistory"
          >
              Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="jobHistory"
          >
            Education
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#schools"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="jobHistory"
          >
            School
          </button>

        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-body">
              Dentsply Implants
            </div>

            <div class="card card-body">
              LabCentrix LLC
            </div>

            <div class="card card-body">
              Inno360
            </div>
          </div>

        <div class="collapse" id="education">
          <div class="card card-body">
            Masters - CS
          </div>

          <div class="card card-body">
            Bachelors - IT

          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="collapse" id="schools">
          <div class="card card-body">
            University of New Haven
          </div>

          <div class="card card-body">
            Rajiv Gandhi Institute of Technology
          </div>
        </div>

        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>